 * Example Output
 * 
 * Is 'java2novice.pdf' allowed file? true
 * Is 'cric.doc' allowed file? true
 * Is 'java.gif' allowed file? false
 * Is 'novice.mp3' allowed file? false
 * Is 'java_2.jpeg' allowed file? false
